# ── 실험 산출물 (각 챕터) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ch1: TF-IDF · BM25 score 분포 · NDCG/MRR 계산 · two-stage pipeline 비교
# Ch2: DPR contrastive curve · in-batch negatives · hard negative mining · SBERT/E5 비교
# Ch3: Cross-encoder vs ColBERT latency · MaxSim 시각화 · PLAID compression
# Ch4: HNSW graph 시각화 · IVF cluster · PQ centroid · LSH bucket · recall-latency curve
# Ch5: RAG pipeline trace · RETRO chunked CCA · Self-RAG reflection token · CRAG fallback
# Ch6: RRF score 결합 · BM25+dense Pareto · SPLADE sparse weight · RankGPT prompt
# Ch7: GraphRAG community detection · ColPali page embedding · long-context vs RAG ablation
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.svg
*.pdf
*.gif
*.mp4
*.webm
*.webp

